=<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to the Course</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #1a1917;
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #DFDFDE;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }
        .wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            table-layout: fixed;
            background-color: #1a1917;
            padding-bottom: 60px;
        }
        .main {
            background-color: #1a1917;
            margin: 0 auto;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            border-spacing: 0;
            color: #DFDFDE;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .course-name {
            color: #15fdf6;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .button-container {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .btn {
            background-color: #15fdf6;
            color: #1a1917;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 35px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 4px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666666;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <center class="wrapper">
        <table class="main" width="100%">
            <tr>
                <td class="content">
                    <h1>Welcome to the Journey!</h1>
                    <p>Hi there,</p>
                    <p>Thank you for enrolling in <span class="course-name">{{ $json.Course_Selected }}</span>. We are excited to help you reach your goals!</p>
                    <p>Get ready! Your class is scheduled to start exactly <strong>30 days</strong> from today. We'll send you more details and access links as we get closer to the launch date.</p>

                    <div class="button-container">
                        <a href="#" class="btn">View Dashboard</a>
                    </div>

                    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #888;">If you have any questions, simply reply to this email.</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="footer">
                    &copy; 2024 Your Academy. All rights reserved.
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </center>
</body>
</html>

